      "text": "Last edit about 3 years ago by svayambhu108\n109\nNeeds Review\n109\nK187 very great now; its accelleration accele rates exponentially. Thus its internal info generation + transfer is so swift that permutations + recombinations are taking place at what must be near their maximum limit. guess one thing I'm saying that is important + maybe the case is: Ditheon is man evolved to bilateral hemispheric parity, + Ditheon is Christ. In which case I am equating the evolutionary leap to bilateral hemispheric",
